neuralNetwork
Class FeedForwardNN

java.lang.Object
  neuralNetwork.FeedForwardNN
Direct Known Subclasses:
CompleteCheckersNN, NeuralNetwork1L, NeuralNetwork2L, NeuralNetwork3L, NeuralNetwork4L, PyramidCheckersNN
public abstract class FeedForwardNN
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract Feed-Forward neural network. It handles inputs, firing of neurons, evaluation boards, and saving and loading neural networks. Subclasses should create the actual neurons, define the topography of the neural network and set the initial weights.

Note: Subclasses should create NeuronLayers whose neurons have inputs from the layer before. The NeuronLayers should be added to the layers list. And the output neuron should have the last NeuronLayer as its inputs.

Version:
1.10 - 26 September 2008
Author:
Amos Yuen
